text: Fulton is a town in Missouri, United States. It is the county seat of Callaway County. It is part of the Jefferson City, Missouri Metropolitan Statistical Area. The population was 12,600 in the 2020 census. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Fulton Area Chamber of Commerce * Fulton, Missouri tourism site Category:Callaway County, Missouri Category:Cities in Missouri Category:County seats in Missouri Category:1825 establishments in the United States Category:1820s establishments in Missouri Category:Settlements in Callaway County, Missouri
